PER CURIAM:Â  William Carson Hopkins, Jr. pled guilty to resisting arrest, 
  possession of a stolen vehicle, and failure to stop for a blue light, second 
  offense.Â  He was sentenced to one year for resisting arrest, five years for 
  possession of a stolen vehicle, and five years for failure to stop, to be served 
